Real Madrid face Atletico Madrid in the Champions League quarter-final second leg on Wednesday night . 
  Real Madrid have not beaten rivals Atletico since winning the final in Lisbon last season . 
  Carlo Ancelotti's side have failed to win any of their last seven games against city rivals . 
  Diego Simeone's men have won four of the last eight games against Real . 
  The two sides drew 0-0 in the first leg of the quarter-finals . 
 